embed.title: How to Regen VM Potato License
embed.description:
If your Challenge code has changed or you are on the new PC and want to reactivate Voicemeeter Potato, you can use your regen code at this link below:

I would make sure to copy your current challenge code, that way you can't type it in wrong!!!

Click the Voicemeeter Logo in the top left and right click on current challenge code. (https://i.imgur.com/XGzX3pW.png)

https://shop.vb-audio.com/en/module/vblicensing/myLicenses
